### ==========================================================
### Mispoti Audio Backend — API Examples
### ==========================================================
### Usar con VS Code REST Client o IntelliJ HTTP Client
### Configure BASE_URL según su entorno

@BASE_URL = http://localhost:3000

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 1. Health Check
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/health

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 2. Request audio extraction (nuevo job)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "lcoqOPaBe9M"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 3. Request audio extraction (video privado — debe fallar)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "dQw4w9WgXcQ"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 4. Request con videoId inválido — 400
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": "corto"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 5. Request con videoId vacío — 400
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "videoId": ""
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 6. Ver estado de un job (reemplazar <JOB_ID>)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/status/<JOB_ID>

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 7. Ver estado de un job inexistente — 404
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/status/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 8. Descargar audio (reemplazar <VIDEO_ID> con uno extraído)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/file/<VIDEO_ID>
Accept: audio/mp4

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 9. Descargar audio con Range (primer MB) — 206 Partial Content
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/file/<VIDEO_ID>
Range: bytes=0-1048575

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 10. Descargar audio inexistente — 404
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/file/aaaaaaaaaaa

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 11. Rate limit test (11 requests rápidos) — el 11° debe dar 429
### ----------------------------------------------------------
# Descomentar y ejecutar 11 veces seguidas rápidamente
# POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/audio/request
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "videoId": "lcoqOPaBe9M"
# }
